<plot>A story of a young boy, Steven. Who suffered a terrible accident that left him paralyzed from the waist down. As a man. Steven's life is moslty spent watching the athletes train at his local athletics track. He dreams of being able to run as they do. A young athlete aware of Steven watching him from the stands, is haunted every night by nightmares of being paralyzed. Who has the freedom? The paralyzed man whom dreams of running?. Or the athlete who dreams he's paralyzed?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?159468</url></doc>
